reviews.text: Station run by morons. On numerous times I've been given the wrong information. And when trains are cancelled and no trains stop at the station, they hide the info boards so ppl have to walk down the steep long slope only to find out there's no trains. #MoreAwarenessNeeded

Best supermarket in Sydenham, bar none. Excellent Turkish style bread, good value butchers and fruit and veg not too bad either. An array of non-perishables, with a particularly good selection of nuts, pulses and jarred pickles. Only small gripe is that they don't stock any decent pasta brands.

Lovely station when the sun is shining, long platforms, plenty of seating. Pleasant little coffee shop too with a good range of snacks, seating area and Monmouth Coffee served at a reasonable price. Almost worth being early for your train or missing it and waiting for the next one.
Great station three train Services stop here
